---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Dermatology Training" description="ACD dermatology training program overview.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Dermatology Training</h1>
    <p>ACD — Australasian College of Dermatologists</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-grid">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">4</div><div class="stat-label">years of practical training required</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">3</div><div class="stat-label">types of workplace-based assessments</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>Dermatology training is highly competitive. Trainees undertake 4 years of practical training in accredited clinical settings under the supervision of practising dermatologists.</p>
    <p>The ACD has a commitment to building the rural and regional dermatology workforce, reflected in selection criteria.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Quick Links</h2>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li><a href="/dermatology/entry">Entry requirements & selection</a></li>
      <li><a href="/dermatology/program">Program requirements & assessments</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
